<p>&nbsp;The journal <em>Ingenieria y Competividad </em>is a nonprofit, scientific and technical publication of Universidad del Valle, and therefore it keeps ethical standards on publications internationally accepted, as well as intellectual property rights of authors according to Colombian legislation.</p>
<p>&nbsp;The journal will take appropriate actions to avoid plagiarism of the articles, and the usage of inappropriate, and fraudulent information through a rigorous evaluation process in order to maintain the integrity in the evaluation and publication process of scientific and technical articles.</p>
<p>Articles that have been published in other media will be removed from the journal and reported to the Editorial Committee, and the editor or editorial board of the Journal in which it was published or plagiarized will also be informed.</p>
<p>&nbsp;If an author or authors decide to withdraw an article from the evaluation process of the Journal, he/they should forward communication addressed to the editor of the Journal, informing his/their decision.</p>
